out_desc_tool: Peabody Picture Vocabulary Test

This subtest assesses children’s knowledge of words and their ability to express the word’s meaning. Of the 25 items, 7 were changed from the original in order to maintain the level of difficulty  e.g., banana instead of clock, cow instead of goat, taka (currency) instead of letter, leader instead of hero, hospital instead of castle, gentle instead of polite, and binoculars instead of microscope.
